data.description: Welcome to your dream home in one of Georgia's Top school districts! Gorgeous 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom Colonial Coming Soon For Sale with several updates!  This home features the following:    *New Paint &  Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring throughout  *Spacious  living room, family room, & dining rooms   *Gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, gorgeous tile backsplash, island, and plenty of cabinet space great for storage.  *All four bedrooms located on the second floor   *Master bedroom with vaulted ceilings, walk-in closet and private master bath   *Separate soaking tub and shower in master bath with upgraded granite counter tops on the vanity  *Other three bedrooms nicely designed also with plenty of closet space  *Huge Fenced back yard with extended patio & upgraded landscaping  *HOA includes swimming pool access  *Home Conveniently located  near the Mall of Georgia with endless shopping, dining,  and top-rated schools in a prime location   *More pictures will be coming soon    Tours will be available to starting 04-26-2024
